  <p>A Nostr client focusing direct message and channel message. The main goal is to have an instant messaging application that is easy on people and has a modern touch.</p>

  <p>Currently support NIP-1,NIP-2,NIP-5,NIP-7,NIP-40,NIP-41,NIP-42.(NIP reference)</p>

  <p>Frontend is a clone of Cinny project which has an elegent and simple interface.</p>

  <p>No backend server is available now. Data are stored on relays based on Nostr protocol.</p>
</blockquote>

